registry.title: iana-tls-cipher-suite-algs YANG Module
registry.registration_rule: See the TLS Cipher Suites registry.
registry.description: New values must not be directly added to the "iana-tls-cipher-suite-algs" YANG module. They must instead be added to the "TLS Cipher Suites" registry in the "Transport Layer Security (TLS) Parameters" registry group .
